POST
/pkm-kalender
Create new PKM kalender


Create a new PKM kalender (validates only 1 active calendar) (Admin only)

Parameters
Try it out
No parameters

Request body

application/json
Example Value
Schema
{
  "tahun": 2026,
  "pkm_ids": [
    1,
    2,
    3
  ],
  "tanggal_mulai_pengajuan": "2026-03-01",
  "tanggal_selesai_pengajuan": "2026-04-30",
